Description: Voice input tool for Ubuntu
 Ubuntu Speak is a voice input utility for the Ubuntu desktop.
 It records audio on a global hotkey, sends it to the Alibaba
 Cloud DashScope ASR service, and copies the recognized text
 to the clipboard.
 .
 This package provides the ubuntu-speak command, a GTK settings
 dialog, and a desktop launcher.
